CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Enhabit Inc provides home health and hospice services in the United States. It offers care where patients prefer it: in their homes. It operates business in two segments: home health and hospice. Its home health agencies provide a comprehensive range of Medicare-certified skilled home health services, including skilled nursing, physical, occupational, and speech therapy, medical social work, and home health aide services.
